00:05:07.100 --> 00:05:11.810 position:56%
Pat McPherson for making this
possible and I'm thrilled to see all

00:05:11.810 --> 00:05:15.920
of you here on a wintery
Saturday afternoon.

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:18.920 position:56%
So thank you for making time for us.

00:05:18.920 --> 00:05:22.600
It's a real honor for the
Country Dance and Song Society

00:05:22.600 --> 00:05:27.300
to present a lecture as part
of the Benjamin Botkin series.

00:05:27.300 --> 00:05:31.880
Benjamin Botkin's work among
other things was concerned

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:38.660 position:56%
with addressing the ways in which
folklore can be a force for a change

00:05:38.660 --> 00:05:42.430
in people's lives and
that it is a living thing

00:05:42.430 --> 00:05:47.210
and that forges a deep connection
